name: Untitled Cube Game
description:
Be the best Cube runner ! , 100's of levels waiting to test your skills ! 📲🔥

Untitled Cube Game will challenge your reaction time and skills with crazy obstacles and jumps in this Cube Run!

Collect all those coins !! Chain Combos! Upgrade your skills! And use your Power Ups!!

⬛◼◾▪️2 GAME MODES▪️◾◼⬛

◾Normal : play 100 levels dodging obstacles to unlock the next difficulty (6 modes from normal to godlike).

If you get to the end you can always generate another 100 levels in the same difficulty or move into the next one!

◾Endless : Beat the best score ! Perform the largest combo and run as far as you can!! Claim your rewards!!
You'll need the help of Power Ups ! (upgradeable).

Get the Untitled Cube Game Challenge ON ! 📲🕹🔥
